<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>

      .cell-time{
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .cell-time-title{
        margin-right: 20px;
        min-width: 35px;
      }
      .cell-item{
        display: flex;
        margin-right: 15px;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .cell-item input{
        width: 70px;
        margin-left: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        height: 25px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <form action="./view/setConfig" method="post" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded">
      <h2>打卡时间随机区间可视化配置</h2>
      <h4>自己看好了设置结果哦,别整个开始时间大于结束时间</h4>
      <mian class="main">
        <div class="set-interval">
          <h3>早上:</h3>
          <div class="cell-row">
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">小时:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="morningHour" value="<%= taskConfig.morning.hour[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="morningHour" value="<%= taskConfig.morning.hour[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">分钟:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="morningMinute" value="<%= taskConfig.morning.minute[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="morningMinute" value="<%= taskConfig.morning.minute[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">秒:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="morningSecond" value="<%= taskConfig.morning.second[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="morningSecond" value="<%= taskConfig.morning.second[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="set-interval">
          <h3>中午:</h3>
          <div class="cell-row">
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">小时:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="noonHour" value="<%= taskConfig.noon.hour[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="noonHour" value="<%= taskConfig.noon.hour[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">分钟:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="noonMinute" value="<%= taskConfig.noon.minute[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="noonMinute" value="<%= taskConfig.noon.minute[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">秒:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="noonSecond" value="<%= taskConfig.noon.second[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="noonSecond" value="<%= taskConfig.noon.second[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="set-interval">
          <h3>晚上:</h3>
          <div class="cell-row">
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">小时:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="nightHour" value="<%= taskConfig.night.hour[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="nightHour" value="<%= taskConfig.night.hour[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">分钟:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number" name="nightMinute"  value="<%= taskConfig.night.minute[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number"  name="nightMinute" value="<%= taskConfig.night.minute[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cell-time">
              <div class="cell-time-title">秒:</div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最小:</span>
                <input type="number"  name="nightSecond"  value="<%= taskConfig.night.second[0] %>" />
              </div>
              <div class="cell-item">
                <span>最大:</span>
                <input type="number" name="nightSecond" value="<%= taskConfig.night.second[1] %>" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit">提交</button>
      </mian>
    </form>
  </body>
</html>
